  "id": "cohen_braaten_yang_cloud_detection",
  "summary": "Detects thick and thin clouds in Sentinel-2 imagery using the Braaten-Cohen-Yang threshold algorithm.",
  "description": "Detects thick and thin clouds in Sentinel-2 L2A imagery using the Braaten-Cohen-Yang algorithm, which applies simple threshold tests on the green band, NDGR (green/red normalized difference), and a SWIR constraint to reduce snow misclassification. Renders thick clouds with a blue tint, thin clouds with a red tint, and clear pixels in natural color. Suitable for cloud masking and quality screening ahead of further environmental data analysis."
